indimail-mta (2.3-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * tcpserver - USE_DLMOPEN env variable to decide if dlmopen() or dlopen() to be called for loading shared library
  * svctool - add option --use-dlmopen to configure tcpserver to use dlmopen() instead of dlopen() to load shared objects
  * fixed smtp plugin by setting PLUGINDIR correctly
  * Fixed dlopen() flags for loading smtp plugins
  * qmailctl - update cdb only when input file date is newer than cdb file
  * svctool - fixed conf_dir variable getting clobbered by create_fifologger, preventing creation of LOGFILTER service variable
  * fixed dlopen/linker errors for smtpd-plugin0 (dnsbl.c)
  * svctool - seperated out qmail, indimail config
  * Renamed controlfiles to controlfiles.q
  * etrn.c - load count_dir() using loadLibrary()
  * moved svctool to qmail-1.03
  * hier.c - renamed cronlist to cronlist.q
  * hier.c - added populated nodnscheck control file
  * hier.c - moved leapsecs.dat, leapsecs.txt to /etc/indimail
  * hier.c - added software license for yahoo domainkeys
  * instcheck.c - removed unused function ci()
  * leapsecs_read.c - moved leapsecs.dat to /etc/indimail
  * updated indimail-mta.spec, qupgrade.sh, qlocal_upgrade.sh, Makefile for v2.3 indimail-mta
  * qmail-lspawn.c - use loadLibrary() to load vauth_open(), vauth_getpw(), vclose(), isvirtualdomain() functions
  * qmail-queue.c - use indimail-mta identifier in received headers
  * qmail-rspawn.c - use loadLibrary() to load vget_real_domain(), is_distributed_domain(), findhost()
  * qmail-send.c, qmail-todo.c - removed non-indimail code
  * qmail-showctl - use loadLibrary() to load indimail code
  * qmail-sql - link with MySQL lib without requirein indimail
  * qregex.c - compile sql code with USE_MYSQL definition
  * svctool, indimail-mta.spec, debian/indimail-mta.preinst - changed homedir of qmaill to /var/log/svc
  * moved cron entries to /etc/cron.d

 -- Manvendra Bhangui <manvendra@indimail.org>  Tue, 23 Jan 2018 22:25:30 +0530
